 模式，重 623g，并自带硅胶键盘膜。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img alt="快速切换" height="461" src="https://img.ithome.com/newsuploadfiles/2024/5/75dedb72-9fea-4d1d-b4c0-f8ec7fa54f55.jpg?x-bce-process=image/format,f_auto" title="Keychron B6 Pro 无线轻薄键盘开售：全尺寸布局 + 剪刀脚按键，售价 271 元" width="1440" /></p><dir><a contenteditable="false" href="https://s.click.taobao.com/t?e=m%3D2%26s%3DAdFWUx3ax8Zw4vFB6t2Z2ueEDrYVVa64yK8Cckff7TVRAdhuF14FMVJK8Pr4gKayJ1gyddu7kN9KudquYbwz7QayRoXI2yHRcOEFtHWyuiQqGPuhWuerXg6KhLeHSnTd9CgRSquDwp8ePzBFM%2B2lUPr10Onlnxg7AcqwlgwnvLT9Umq014SDk7ICKXNVhWYiTbm8pUJZ2beDtophDxWhcFSyN7fcQFKgZMHvasZW34dlfdpv7yFScLmFbjEr6RjtRnJjCD35yH5kWOakepAjtTj5%2BKsGvHuYzsAzH1xYDH73YRnnT1tpK3%2FP7gcFmwYRDseal0NfMDXJpWvVCAyWdKJn5AyUbPoV&amp;union_lens=lensId:TAPI@1720528320@213f13ee_1378_190977ab8fc_ceca@01" target="_blank"><span class="card main-site"><span class="card-logo"><img height="800" src="https://img.alicdn.com/bao/uploaded/i3/2208307283070/O1CN01ASKTBh1YY6tLxUvix_!!0-item_pic.jpg" title="Keychron B6 Pro 无线轻薄键盘开售：全尺寸布局 + 剪刀脚按键，售价 271 元" width="800" /></span><span class="card-info"><span class="card-title"><span class="mall-data">天猫</span><span class="card-name"> Keychron B6 Pro 无线轻薄键盘</span></span><span class="card-abstract"></span><span class="card-controls"><span class="price"> 271 元</span><span class="card-btn-deep">直达链接</span></span></span></span></a></dir><p class="ad-tips">广告声明：文内含有的对外跳转链接（包括不限于超链接、二维码、口令等形式），用于传递更多信息，节省甄选时间，结果仅供参考，IT之家所有文章均包含本声明。</p>
